msgctxt "sn55.11:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 55 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 55 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: 2. Rājakārāmavagga → sahassa or rājakārāmavaggo (pts1)
msgctxt "sn55.11:0.2"
msgid "2. Rājakārāmavagga "
msgstr "2. A Thousand Nuns "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 11. Sahassabhikkhunisaṅghasutta → sahassasuttaṃ (bj) | sahassa (pts1)
msgctxt "sn55.11:0.3"
msgid "11. Sahassabhikkhunisaṅghasutta "
msgstr "11. A Saṅgha of a Thousand Nuns "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn55.11:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati rājakārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in the Royal Monastery. "

#. VAR: sahassabhikkhunisaṃgho → sahassaṃ bhikkhunīsaṃgho (bj) | sahassabhikkhunīsaṅgho (s1-3)
msgctxt "sn55.11:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho sahassabhikkhunisaṃgho yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho tā bhikkhuniyo bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then a Saṅgha of a thousand nuns went up to the Buddha, bowed, and stood to one side. The Buddha said to them: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.361, sc2
msgctxt "sn55.11:2.1"
msgid "“Catūhi kho, bhikkhuniyo, dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako sotāpanno hoti avinipātadhammo niyato sambodhiparāyaṇo. "
msgstr "“Nuns, a noble disciple who has four things is a stream-enterer, not liable to be reborn in the underworld, bound for awakening. "

msgctxt "sn55.11:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn55.11:2.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhuniyo, ariyasāvako buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti—"
msgstr "It’s when a noble disciple has experiential confidence in the Buddha … "

msgctxt "sn55.11:2.4"
msgid "itipi so bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavāti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn55.11:2.5"
msgid "Dhamme … pe … "
msgstr "the teaching … "

msgctxt "sn55.11:2.6"
msgid "saṅghe … pe … "
msgstr "the Saṅgha … "

msgctxt "sn55.11:2.7"
msgid "ariyakantehi sīlehi samannāgato hoti, akhaṇḍehi … pe … samādhisaṃvattanikehi. "
msgstr "And they have the ethical conduct loved by the noble ones … leading to immersion. "

msgctxt "sn55.11:2.8"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhuniyo, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako sotāpanno hoti avinipātadhammo niyato sambodhiparāyaṇo”ti. "
msgstr "A noble disciple who has these four things is a stream-enterer, not liable to be reborn in the underworld, bound for awakening.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.11:2.9"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

